fields.title: The New Open Build
fields.body: Open Build is continuing to support communities and STEAM education in developing countries, but through our partners we are beginning a new phase of training and hiring open source software developers.   With this new direction we believe we can help more small business and local organizations in the communities we work in, while also educating and growing the open source community.  Watch for more updates to come.

fields.body:
Open Build is continuing to support communities and STEAM education in developing countries, but through our partners we are beginning a new phase of training and hiring open source software developers.

With this new direction we believe we can help more small business and local organizations in the communities we work in, while also educating and growing the open source community.

Watch for more updates to come.
